channel.title: Could anyone help me with somthing please?
channel.description:
hi, ive been trying to make shops for my server it just wont work ive tried 4 diffrent tuts while ive been looking through the tutorial page anywayz each one i get this error ive tried putting in the xrange and yrange but it wont work ive tried leaving it out too thig is my copiler dosent get the error its when i use the runserver it says this [code]Starting pimpscape Server on 0.0.0.0:5555 Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NumberFormatException: For input string: "2 474 2835 2981 0 1 frog prince" at java.lang.NumberFormatException.forInputString(NumberFormatException. java:48) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Integer.java:456) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Integer.java:497) at NPCHandler.loadAutoSpawn(NPCHandler.java:1279) at NPCHandler.<init>(NPCHandler.java:23) at server.main(server.java:27) [/code] if someone could help me on this it would be great help thanks alot.
smokin_acez
